title: current_maildir()
brief: Retrieve the currently selected folder.
----


<p>When in maildir mode, set with <a href="global_mode.html">global_mode</a>, the user interface consists of a list of maildir folders.</p>
<p>This function will retrieve the full path to the currently highlighted folder.</p>
<p>For example: </p>
<pre>
-- Show folder:
msg( current_maildir() );
</pre>
<p class="seealso">See also <a href="selected_folders.html">selected_folders()</a>.</p>
